data.text: @WillNissen2 @stephen_galli @DaveBautista @prattprattpratt @karengillan @zoesaldana They need to be as vocal - that’s the point - Dave is a stand up guy, but he’s doesn’t have the weight of Pratt of Saldana or really even Gillian - he’s on his way there, but he’s not there yet.
